\begin_layout Standard
SMAZ
\begin_inset CommandInset citation
LatexCommand cite
key "SMAZ"

\end_inset

 is the only other open-source short-message compression library known to
 the authors.
 SMAZ is remarkable in that its complete implementation is less than 200
 lines of code --- which includes the code book of common character sequences
 that performs the role of the pre-computed dictionary.
 The README file for SMAZ claims average reduction in message length to
 50% --- 60% of original size, with English text compressing better.
 
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
The performance of SMAZ on the three English text TS03.42 sample messages
 suggests that the claim of reducing messages to an average of 50% --- 60%
 of original size may not hold true for SMS-type traffic.
 As the implementation of SMAZ is freely available it is possible to test
 this claim.
 
\end_layout

