 Attempt was made to include the National University of Singapore (NUS)
 SMS corpus, the largest public SMS corpus known to the authors.
 The NUS corpus custodians did not respond in time for inclusion of the
 NUS corpus in this comparison.
 SMS SPAM Collection v.1
